citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:15am-11:45am
on 25-JUL-2023. Inspector arrived at site and called licensee, there was no answer and no way to leave a message. The
inspector knocked on the door with no response, he then left a flyer and waited 30 minutes. The inspector then called the
number on file with no response, The inspector then left the site.
End Section
